<D>__{what?}
<C>__{mr. johnny}
<D>__{will you marry me?}
<C>__{loretta}
<D>__{bobo, take the cart away.}
<A>__{he does.}
<C>__{loretta}
<P>__{(continuing)}
<D>__{are you proposing marriage to me?}
<C>__{mr. johnny}
<D>__{yes?}
<C>__{loretta}
<D>__{you know i was married and that my husband died. but what you don't know is i think he and i had bad luck.}
<C>__{mr. johnny}
<D>__{what do you mean?}
