<P>__{(at a loss)}
<D>__{the ring?}
<A>__{bob and mook are watching mr. johnny's performance they are deadpan mugs.}
<C>__{bob}
<P>__{(to mr. johnny)}
<D>__{a ring. that's right.}
<C>__{mook}
<D>__{i woulda sprung for a ring if it was me.}
<B>__{bobo and eddie stand near the kitchen watching}
<C>__{bobo}
<D>__{she's got him on his knees. he's ruining his suit.}
